d:
Release 370. Taking a short break from John K Pe-ta stuff to bring the next and final chapter of something I released back in November. This is the chapter I really wanted due to the Yuri, but I had mistakenly though that the previous chapter was part of this story. I know they're all of a story, but you know what I mean.

To that end, I have no plans of releasing anything else form this book. If anyone else wants to jump in, you have my blessing.
